description: Added interactive Licensing Roadmap page with expand/collapse tree for CA DRE and DOI certification paths. Wired Roadmap into navigation, App routing, types, routes.config, and Sitemap resolver. Fixed React 19 compliance: replaced all React.ReactNode, React.ChangeEvent, and React.FormEvent namespace references with proper named type imports (ReactNode, ChangeEvent, FormEvent) compatible with react-jsx automatic transform.
